org.mitre.tdp.boogie.alg.approach.impl

Class AllApproachPredictor

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.mitre.tdp.boogie.alg.approach.impl.AllApproachPredictor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ApproachPredictor

    public class AllApproachPredictor
extends java.lang.Object
implements ApproachPredictor
    "Predicts" all of the available approach procedures at the airport. When used this will read into the final LegGraph all of the procedures at the given airport resolving which to fly via the shortest path algorithm.
